          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1387.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, remove the tray from the oven and leave the<strong>&nbsp;pie</strong> to&nbsp;cool&nbsp;slightly for a few min&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Serve the<strong>&nbsp;potato-topped&nbsp;chicken, mustard &amp; kale pie</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
